Package com.app.collectors.generic

Class CollectorGeneric<T,U,W>

java.lang.Object
com.app.collectors.generic.CollectorGeneric<T,U,W>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of input elements to the collector.
U - The type of elements in the intermediate list.
W - The type of the result produced by the collector.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collector<T,List<U>,W>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CarMinMaxCollector, CarStatisticCollector
public abstract class CollectorGeneric<T,U,W> extends Object implements Collector<T,List<U>,W>
A generic implementation of the Collector interface. This abstract class provides a basic implementation of a Collector that collects elements of type T into a list of type U and then produces a result of type W.
